00:24:09.370 --> 00:24:13.350
Now the first time I read this
recipe my only thought was, huh?

00:24:13.350 --> 00:24:17.820
I had no idea what it
was even talking about.

00:24:17.820 --> 00:24:21.150
Anybody want to hazard a guess

00:24:21.150 --> 00:24:24.770
of what time period this
recipe may have come from?

