So it's -- this -- I mean
it's basically just cornmeal

00:25:17.660 --> 00:25:20.480
and milk and molasses.

00:25:20.480 --> 00:25:23.230
So it would have been
things that, in the South,

00:25:23.230 --> 00:25:24.760
they would have had on the farm.

